INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (2,2,'Mais ACEM TECH cest quoi quoi?','Solution innovante dont le simple but est de garantir lenrichissement et la valorisation des projets innovants, de cultiver lesprit dinnovation, développer et faciliter lesprit dépanouissement.','<p><strong>L&rsquo;ACEM TECH est une solution innovante dont le simple but est&nbsp;de garantir l&rsquo;enrichissement et la valorisation des projets innovants, de cultiver l&rsquo;esprit d&rsquo;innovation, d&eacute;velopper et faciliter l&rsquo;esprit d&rsquo;&eacute;panouissement.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cette plateforme a pour objectif&nbsp;:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- De rendre visible et accessible des projets et recherches &eacute;dit&eacute;es par des &eacute;tudiants comoriens &agrave; but non lucratif, toutes disciplines confondues (sciences exactes et naturelles, sciences humaines et sociales&hellip;).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- De diffuser des ressources documentaires et archivistiques et fournir&nbsp;l&rsquo;expertise et les outils pour r&eacute;pondre aux besoins d&rsquo;information de sa communaut&eacute;. Sous la responsabilit&eacute; d&#39;un membre du bureau Ex&eacute;cutif de l&rsquo;ACEM, L&rsquo;ACEM TECH, assume notamment les responsabilit&eacute;s suivantes :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Favoriserl&rsquo;avancement et la diffusion du savoir, en soutien &agrave; l&rsquo;enseignement et &agrave; la recherche, en d&eacute;veloppant des collections sous tous les formats et en offrant l&rsquo;acc&egrave;s &agrave; distance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Participer &agrave; la r&eacute;ussite &eacute;tudiante en collaborant avec le personnel enseignant au d&eacute;veloppement des comp&eacute;tences informationnelles des &eacute;tudiantes et des &eacute;tudiants.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Assurer l&rsquo;acquisition, l&rsquo;organisation et la conservation des documents incluant des fonds d&rsquo;archives priv&eacute;es.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- D&eacute;velopper des services et des outils technologiques facilitant la d&eacute;couverte de l&rsquo;information et de la documentation sous tous les formats.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Offrir &agrave; l&rsquo;ensemble de la communaut&eacute; universitaire les ressources n&eacute;cessaires pour l&rsquo;utilisation des &oelig;uvres d&rsquo;autrui dans le respect de la l&eacute;gislation sur le droit d&rsquo;auteur.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- G&eacute;rer et planifier des espaces stimulants qui r&eacute;pondent &agrave; l&rsquo;&eacute;volution des besoins de la communaut&eacute; universitaire.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>A PROPOS DE L&#39;ACEM MAROC</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>L&#39; association des comoriens &eacute;tudiant au Maroc (ACEM) est une association qui entre dans le cadre estudiantin, sociale, scientifique, culturel et aussi religieux.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Depuis 2002, l&#39; ACEM organise chaque ann&eacute;e des activit&eacute;s scientifiques et culturelles dans le but de sensibliser le maximum possible tous les &eacute;tudiants comoriens se trouvant dans l&#39;ensemble du royaume. Parmi ces activit&eacute;s, on distingue la journ&eacute;e culturelle scientifique. Cette derni&egrave;re est la plus &eacute;minente de toutes par son envergure et son importance aupr&egrave;s de tout un chacun.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>VOUS ETES DEVELOPPEUR, WEBMASTER? VOULEZ-VOUS AIDER, CONTRIBUEZ?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Si vous pensez &ecirc;tre capable de nous aider &agrave; am&eacute;liorer le projet par tout les moyens possibles, merci de nous contacter via mail: <strong>geeks@acem.tech</strong>. Etant un projet purement open source, vous pourrez contribuer au projet sur GitHub.</p>\r\n','Communiques','01adba9a4d45d8f14e69da1b7c24660a7af4f54e.jpeg','2022-02-12 19:45:58','Logo de l&#39; ACEM TECH'),(3,3,'Conception et Realisation d&#39;un parking Rotatif','Lobjectif du projet est doptimiser la surface horizontale en exploitant la hauteur et gérer les places de manière intelligente tout en optimisant le temps du cycle.','<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <b>Contexte G&eacute;n&eacute;ral du projet :</b></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Depuis plusieurs ann&eacute;es le nombre de voiture dans nos villes ne cesse de croitre. Le&nbsp;stationnement des voitures dans plusieurs villes est devenu un v&eacute;ritable&nbsp;probl&egrave;me en raison du nombre important des voitures et l&#39;insuffisance des espaces des stationnements, ce qui entraine un&nbsp;bouchonnement des villes. Le parking Rotatif est un syst&egrave;me de stationnement rotatif qui au point de vue de l&acute;espace et du prix repr&eacute;sente une solution effective pour le probl&egrave;me de stationnement urbain d&acute;aujourd&acute;hui. Il a&nbsp;de petites dimensions horizontales avec la surface &agrave;&nbsp;peu pr&egrave;s de deux places de parking.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Le parking Rotatif est propos&eacute; au regard des co&ucirc;ts tr&egrave;s modiques du servis et du maintien. Il est possible d&acute;y parquer des voitures de tourisme et aussi des SUV. La commande du syst&egrave;me de stationnement du parking rotatif est assur&eacute;e par l&acute;interm&eacute;diaire de l&acute;&eacute;cran de contact, de la carte d&acute;identification ou de la puce. C&acute;est un syst&egrave;me tr&egrave;s intuitif, facile &agrave; man&oelig;uvrer et n&acute;exige pas aucune personne autoris&eacute;e &agrave; la manipulation. Les utilisateurs peuvent aussi r&eacute;server leur place de parking par l&acute;internet.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Des variantes individuelles du syst&egrave;me du parking rotatif&nbsp;contiennent de 6 &agrave; 16 voitures. D&acute;un point de vue m&eacute;canique, il s&#39;agit d&acute;une construction librement plac&eacute;e avec une dur&eacute;e de vie plus de 20 ans et avec une installation rapide d&eacute;j&agrave; de 3 jours en fonction du mod&egrave;le.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; text-indent:35.4pt; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Objectif du projet :</span></span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">L&rsquo;objectif du projet est d&rsquo;optimiser la surface horizontale en exploitant la hauteur et g&eacute;rer les places de mani&egrave;re intelligente tout&nbsp;en optimisant le temps du cycle.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px; text-align:justify; text-indent:35.4pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"background:#fafafa\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">Principe de fonctionnement </span></span></span></span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"background:#fafafa\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">Le syst&egrave;me de stationnement rotatif vertical effectue un mouvement circulaire dans la direction verticale du sol. Son principe de fonctionnement consiste &agrave; activer le m&eacute;canisme d&#39;entra&icirc;nement par moteur &agrave; engrenages, les supports de voiture sont install&eacute;s &agrave; intervalles r&eacute;guliers sur la cha&icirc;ne de traction, &agrave; travers le mouvement du cycle pour acc&eacute;der au v&eacute;hicule</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"Table\" style=\"width:878px; background:#fafafa; border-collapse:collapse\" width=\"0\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #eeeeee; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; background-color:#fafafa; border-top:1px solid #eeeeee; border-right:1px solid #eeeeee; border-left:1px solid #eeeeee\" valign=\"bottom\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <b>&Eacute;quipement de stationnement rotatif vertical</b></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #eeeeee; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; background-color:#fafafa; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid #eeeeee; border-left:1px solid #eeeeee\" valign=\"bottom\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">Dispositif de s&eacute;curit&eacute;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #eeeeee; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; background-color:#fafafa; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid #eeeeee; border-left:none\" valign=\"bottom\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">Frein d&#39;urgence, d&eacute;tection de sur-longueur, m&eacute;canisme de d&eacute;tection de personnes ou de voiture entrant</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #eeeeee; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; background-color:#fafafa; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid #eeeeee; border-left:1px solid #eeeeee\" valign=\"bottom\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">Mode de fonctionnement</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #eeeeee; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; background-color:#fafafa; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid #eeeeee; border-left:none\" valign=\"bottom\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">Bouton / carte IC</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #eeeeee; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; background-color:#fafafa; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid #eeeeee; border-left:1px solid #eeeeee\" valign=\"bottom\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">DIMENSION DE LA VOITURE</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #eeeeee; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; background-color:#fafafa; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid #eeeeee; border-left:none\" valign=\"bottom\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">&le;5300 mm * 2000 mm * 1550 mm</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #eeeeee; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; background-color:#fafafa; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid #eeeeee; border-left:1px solid #eeeeee\" valign=\"bottom\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">QUANTIT&Eacute; DE VOITURE</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #eeeeee; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; background-color:#fafafa; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid #eeeeee; border-left:none\" valign=\"bottom\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">&le;150S</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #eeeeee; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; background-color:#fafafa; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid #eeeeee; border-left:1px solid #eeeeee\" valign=\"bottom\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">ENTRER M&Eacute;THODE</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #eeeeee; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; background-color:#fafafa; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid #eeeeee; border-left:none\" valign=\"bottom\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">ENTR&Eacute;E AVANT, SORTIE ARRI&Egrave;RE</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #eeeeee; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; background-color:#fafafa; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid #eeeeee; border-left:1px solid #eeeeee\" valign=\"bottom\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">SYST&Egrave;ME DE FREINAGE</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #eeeeee; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; background-color:#fafafa; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid #eeeeee; border-left:none\" valign=\"bottom\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">SYST&Egrave;ME DE FREINAGE AC NORMALEMENT FERM&Eacute;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"background:#fafafa\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">1) Adopter une technologie de pointe</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"background:#fafafa\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">2) Il est pratique et rapide de ranger la voiture, et il faut 20 secondes &agrave; chaque v&eacute;hicule pour stocker et d&eacute;poser le v&eacute;hicule;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"background:#fafafa\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">3) Convertisseur de fr&eacute;quence de configuration, toute la machine fonctionne plus facilement, &eacute;conomise de l&#39;&eacute;lectricit&eacute;, r&eacute;duit la consommation d&#39;&eacute;nergie, le bruit est faible;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"background:#fafafa\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">4) Dispositif anti-oscillation de stationnement de chargement pour emp&ecirc;cher efficacement l&#39;oscillation de la plaque de charge;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"background:#fafafa\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"color:black\">5) Facile &agrave; assembler et &agrave; d&eacute;placer, &agrave; l&#39;aide de la man&oelig;uvre automatique PLC, le v&eacute;hicule d&#39;acc&egrave;s intelligent peut-&ecirc;tre compl&eacute;ter avec une carte magn&eacute;tique.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; text-indent:18.0pt; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Mat&eacute;riels utilis&eacute;s pour la r&eacute;alisation du projet :</span></span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Carte arduino Uno</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Servomoteur</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Leds</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Beadbord</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Fils de connexion</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Capteur infrarouge TCRT5000</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Capteur infrarouge receveur</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">T&eacute;l&eacute;commande&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Moteur pas &agrave; pas 28BYJ-48</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Ecran LCD 16*2</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Carton</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">R&eacute;alisateurs du projet :</span></span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">MOHAMED M&rsquo;MADI HASSANE (Ing&eacute;nieur en Conception M&eacute;canique et Innovation)</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">ABDEREMANE IBRAHIM AHMED (Etudiant en Master 2 Syst&egrave;mes Intelligents et Energie)</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">SOIFAOU MOHAMED DJAE (&Eacute;l&egrave;ve ing&eacute;nieur en 3&egrave;me ann&eacute;e G&eacute;nie Civil)</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n','Projets','a3bc0b0da168b89594944fcf7fcdabc5918a62fc.jpg','2022-02-13 21:15:12','Prototype du projet'),(4,4,'Maison intelligente (Smart Home)','Chaque être humain rêve davoir un logement encore plus confortable, une bonne température dans chaque pièce, un éclairage adapté, une surveillance à distance. Ainsi, la domotique ...','<p><strong>Contexte g&eacute;n&eacute;ral&nbsp;du projet:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Chaque &ecirc;tre humain r&ecirc;ve d&rsquo;avoir un logement encore plus confortable, une bonne temp&eacute;rature dans chaque pi&egrave;ce, un &eacute;clairage adapt&eacute;, une surveillance &agrave; distance.</p>\n\n<p>Ainsi, la domotique n&rsquo;est pas seulement un jouet pour les passionn&eacute;s de technologie, mais aussi pour les personnes moins dou&eacute;es, la possibilit&eacute; de contr&ocirc;ler leur maison. En domotique, trois domaines sont au centre de l&rsquo;attention : la s&eacute;curit&eacute;, l&rsquo;&eacute;conomie de l&rsquo;&eacute;nergie et le confort des r&eacute;sidents. La domotique ouvre non seulement de nouvelles possibilit&eacute;s dans le domaine de l&rsquo;automatisation de l&rsquo;habitation, mais constitue aussi et surtout un moyen offert &agrave; l&rsquo;individu de contr&ocirc;ler et de g&eacute;rer son environnement. Gr&acirc;ce &agrave; cette nouvelle technologie, l&rsquo;habitant sera &agrave; m&ecirc;me de mieux g&eacute;rer son milieu de travail et de vie sur le plan de la s&eacute;curit&eacute;, du confort, des communications et des applications m&eacute;nag&egrave;res.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Objectif du projet:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Ce projet consiste &agrave; r&eacute;aliser un prototype d&rsquo;une maison intelligente avec la carte Raspberry Pi qui ne cesse de donner des solutions facile pour le domaine de la domotique.</p>\n\n\n<p><strong>Mat&eacute;riels utilis&eacute;s:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Carte arduino Mega</li>\n	<li>Breadbord</li>\n	<li>Leds</li>\n	<li>Fils de connexion</li>\n	<li>Module Bluetooth (HC-06)</li>\n	<li>Servomoteur</li>\n	<li>Clavier matriciel</li>\n	<li>Bouton poussoir</li>\n	<li>Capteur de mouvement (PIR)</li>\n	<li>Capteur LDR</li>\n	<li>Ecran LCD 16 *4</li>\n	<li>Ventilateur</li>\n	<li>Capteur de temp&eacute;rature LM35</li>\n	<li>Capteur de flamme ST060</li>\n	<li>Buzzer</li>\n	<li>Carton&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Application pour la commande Bluetooth (App MIT inventor)</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<p>Veuillez trouvez le code arduino du projet <a href=\"https://github.com/acemtech/maison_intelligente\">ici</a></p>\n<br>\n<p><strong>R&eacute;alisateur du projet&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>ABDEREMANE IBRAHIM AHMED (Etudiant en Master 2 Syst&egrave;mes Intelligents et Energie)</li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://acemtech.org/utilisateurs/profile/3\"> MOHAMED M&rsquo;MADI HASSANE</a> (Ing&eacute;nieur en Conception M&eacute;canique et Innovation)</li>\n	<li>SOIFAOU MOHAMED DJAE (&Eacute;l&egrave;ve ing&eacute;nieur en 3&egrave;me ann&eacute;e G&eacute;nie Civil)</li>\n</ul>','Projets','cca75df206799d81ebdbee81eef97758a064bb51.jpg','2022-02-13 22:03:44','Prototype du projet'),(5,2,'SOUTENANCE DE THESE DE DOCTORAT','L&#39; ACEMTECH, vous invite à prendre par au soutenance de Mr Moussa Omar Saanyane, ex président de lACEM, qui aura lieu le 24 Mars 2022, à la FSJES de Salé à partir 10h.','<p><strong>Soutenance de th&egrave;se :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>La soutenance est &agrave; la fois un rituel de passage, un moment inoubliable et une source de stress sans nom.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>L&#39; acemtech, est heureux de vous annoncer la soutenance de <strong>Mr Moussa Omar Saanyane</strong>, <em>Ex President de l&rsquo;ACEM</em>, qui aura lieu le 24 Mars 2022, &agrave; la FSJES de Sal&eacute; &agrave; partir 10h.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>L&#39; acemtech tient &agrave; souhaiter bonne chance audit th&eacute;sard. La pr&eacute;sence de tout un chacun est vivement souhait&eacute;e.</p>\r\n','Communiques','1c1f1991fbd16ec300ba490730f75414aebee25c.jpg','2022-03-23 16:21:55','Dr Moussa Omar Saanyane entouré des membres du jury de la soutenance à la faculté d&#39;économie de Salé el-jadida'),(6,3,'Suiveur Solaire','En 2015, le marché mondial de 4 GW installés est dominé par des entreprises américaines, dans l&#39;ordre Array Technologies, Sunpower, First Solar et Nextracker. Les français Exosun et Optimum ...','<p style=\"border:none; margin-bottom:4px; text-align:justify; padding:0cm\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Contexte g&eacute;n&eacute;ral </span></span></b></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Un&nbsp;</span></span></span><b style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal; text-align:start; text-decoration-thickness:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial\">tracker solaire</b><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal; text-align:start\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><span style=\"float:none\">,&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span><b style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal; text-align:start; text-decoration-thickness:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial\">traqueur solaire</b><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal; text-align:start\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><span style=\"float:none\">&nbsp;ou&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span><b style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal; text-align:start; text-decoration-thickness:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial\">suiveur de Soleil</b><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal; text-align:start\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><span style=\"float:none\">&nbsp;est un dispositif permettant &agrave; un t&eacute;lescope h&eacute;liographique&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal; text-align:start\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><span style=\"float:none\">(devant observer le soleil ou certains de ses effets dans l&#39;atmosph&egrave;re</span></span></span></span></span><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" style=\"unicode-bidi:isolate; font-variant-ligatures:normal; text-align:start; text-decoration-thickness:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial\"><a href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tracker_solaire#cite_note-1\" style=\"color:blue; text-decoration:underline\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"text-underline:none\">1</span></span></a></sup><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal; text-align:start\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><span style=\"float:none\">), ou &agrave; une installation de production d&rsquo;&eacute;nergie soalire</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal; text-align:start\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><span style=\"float:none\">&nbsp;de suivre le soleil selon le principe de l&#39;h&eacute;liostat</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal; text-align:start\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><span style=\"float:none\">. Cette structure portante motoris&eacute;e oriente les panneaux solaires</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal; text-align:start\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><span style=\"float:none\">&nbsp;pour en augmenter la productivit&eacute;.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom:solid #a2a9b1 1.0pt; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n<p style=\"border:none; margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:4px; text-align:justify; padding:0cm\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Principe de fonctionnement</span></span></b></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:8px; margin-bottom:8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Le syst&egrave;me vise &agrave; orienter en temps r&eacute;el les capteurs vers le Soleil, pour placer le panneau dans une position optimale par rapport &agrave; l&#39;incidence du rayonnement solaire (perpendiculaire au rayonnement si possible), car tout au long de la journ&eacute;e et de l&#39;ann&eacute;e (selon les saisons) la position du soleil varie constamment et d&#39;une mani&egrave;re diff&eacute;rente selon la latitude. Cette adaptation en temps r&eacute;el a pour effet de substantiellement augmenter la captation et production d&#39;&eacute;nergie.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:8px; margin-bottom:8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Elle peut se faire sur deux axes&nbsp;: en azimut&nbsp;(d&#39;est en ouest, &agrave; mesure de l&#39;avanc&eacute;e de la journ&eacute;e) et en hauteur&nbsp;(selon la saison et, de nouveau, l&#39;avanc&eacute;e de la journ&eacute;e). L&#39;id&eacute;al est d&#39;utiliser un tracker &agrave; deux axes, mais il en existe aussi avec un seul (typiquement avec un suivi seulement en azimut, l&#39;angle par rapport au sol &eacute;tant fix&eacute; selon l&#39;optimum local, qui d&eacute;pend de la latitude)<sup><a href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tracker_solaire#cite_note-2\" style=\"color:blue; text-decoration:underline\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"text-underline:none\">2</span></span></a></sup>.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom:solid #a2a9b1 1.0pt; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n<p style=\"border:none; margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:4px; text-align:justify; padding:0cm\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Gains attendus</span></span></b></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:8px; margin-bottom:8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">En zone temp&eacute;r&eacute;e, l&#39;augmentation de performance entre les panneaux fixes correctement orient&eacute;s (orient&eacute;s plein sud) et les trackers varie de 30&nbsp;% &agrave; 45&nbsp;% selon le type de tracker, voire plus par moments (H&eacute;lioslite annonce +43&nbsp;% d&#39;&eacute;nergie produite, avec une pointe &agrave; +57&nbsp;% sur une journ&eacute;e pour un tracker deux axes&nbsp;; ex&nbsp;: 45,6 kWh en une journ&eacute;e, contre 28,8 kWh pour un capteur fixe de m&ecirc;me puissance (6 kWc) en Savoie)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom:solid #a2a9b1 1.0pt; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n<p style=\"border:none; margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:4px; text-align:justify; padding:0cm\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">M&eacute;canisme de suivi</span></span></b></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:8px; margin-bottom:8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Il peut s&#39;agir d&#39;un m&eacute;canisme d&#39;horlogerie (en un lieu donn&eacute;, la meilleure direction d&#39;orientation ne d&eacute;pend que de l&#39;heure et de la date) ou d&#39;un dispositif d&#39;asservissement. La puissance n&eacute;cessaire est toujours tr&egrave;s faible (quelques watts) et ne constitue pas un inconv&eacute;nient. Il existe deux principales mani&egrave;res d&#39;orienter un panneau solaire de fa&ccedil;on optimale: une installation de quatre photor&eacute;sistances dont la tension &agrave; leurs bornes doit &ecirc;tre &eacute;gale pour &ecirc;tre face au soleil, ou la programmation au pr&eacute;alable de l&#39;&eacute;quation de la trajectoire du soleil pour diriger correctement le panneau.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom:solid #a2a9b1 1.0pt; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n<p style=\"border:none; margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:4px; text-align:justify; padding:0cm\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Types et quantit&eacute;s de panneaux</span></span></b></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:8px; margin-bottom:8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Un tracker peut, en th&eacute;orie, porter des modules solaires de n&#39;importe quel type&nbsp;: modules photovolta&iuml;ques&nbsp;(PV) &quot;classique&quot; , CPV (photovolta&iuml;ques&nbsp;concetr&eacute;&nbsp;) ou CSP (thermique&nbsp;: Tour ou Stirling). Mais, en pratique, seuls quelques trackers le peuvent car les co&ucirc;ts induits (investissement sup&eacute;rieur) sont &eacute;lev&eacute;s et les inconv&eacute;nients (maintenance, risques suppl&eacute;mentaires) nombreux.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:8px; margin-bottom:8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Chaque tracker peut supporter de 4 &agrave; 220 m&sup2; de panneaux. En 2015-2016 apparaissent de nouveaux mod&egrave;les plus l&eacute;gers (ex&nbsp;: 200 kg au lieu de 550 kg pour 3,3 kW en 10 modules photovolta&iuml;ques) pr&eacute;sent&eacute;s comme robustes, moins couteux, plus performants et pouvant r&eacute;pondre aux besoins d&#39;autoconsommation et &ecirc;tre install&eacute;s sur une toiture plate.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom:solid #a2a9b1 1.0pt; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n<p style=\"border:none; margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:4px; text-align:justify; padding:0cm\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Sp&eacute;cificit&eacute;s</span></span></b></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:8px; margin-bottom:8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Les principales caract&eacute;ristiques diff&eacute;renciant les trackers sont les suivantes&nbsp;:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:2px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Le gain en production &eacute;lectrique (par rapport &agrave; des panneaux solaires fixes)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:2px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">L&#39;orientation mono ou multi axiale</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:2px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">La pr&eacute;cision du positionnement vis-&agrave;-vis du soleil (type d&#39;asservissement), &eacute;ventuellement en pr&eacute;sence d&#39;ombre port&eacute;e&nbsp;<sup><a href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tracker_solaire#cite_note-3\" style=\"color:blue; text-decoration:underline\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"text-underline:none\">3</span></span></a></sup>.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:2px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">La robustesse (tenue au vent) et la fiabilit&eacute;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:2px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Le co&ucirc;t</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom:solid #a2a9b1 1.0pt; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n<p style=\"border:none; margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:4px; text-align:justify; padding:0cm\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">March&eacute;</span></span></b></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:8px; margin-bottom:8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">En 2015, le march&eacute; mondial de 4&nbsp;GW&nbsp;install&eacute;s est domin&eacute; par des entreprises am&eacute;ricaines, dans l&#39;ordre Array Technologies, Sunpower, First Solar&nbsp;et Nextracker. Les fran&ccedil;ais Exosun&nbsp;et Optimum Tracker commencent &agrave; peine leur activit&eacute; &agrave; l&#39;&eacute;tranger<sup><a href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tracker_solaire#cite_note-4\" style=\"color:blue; text-decoration:underline\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"text-underline:none\">4</span></span></a></sup>. Le secteur se consolide les ann&eacute;es suivantes, en parall&egrave;le d&#39;une croissance amenant &agrave; 14,5&nbsp;GW&nbsp;vendus en 2017<sup><a href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tracker_solaire#cite_note-5\" style=\"color:blue; text-decoration:underline\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"text-underline:none\">5</span></span></a></sup>.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom:solid #a2a9b1 1.0pt; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n<p style=\"border:none; margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:4px; text-align:justify; padding:0cm\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Mat&eacute;riels utilis&eacute;s pour la r&eacute;alisation du projet </span></span></b></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Carte arduino</span></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"> <b>Uno</b>&nbsp;: Le microcontr&ocirc;leur qui est le cerveau du syst&egrave;me </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Servomoteurs</span></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">&nbsp;: 2 servomoteurs pour la rotation &agrave; deux axes </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Leds</span></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">&nbsp;: 2&nbsp;Leds utilis&eacute;s pour indiquer que le syst&egrave;me fonctionne ou non &nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Beadbord&nbsp;</span></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">: Utilis&eacute;e pour d&eacute;velopper un circuit &eacute;lectronique et un c&acirc;blage avec la carte microcontr&ocirc;leur Arduino</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Fils de connexion</span></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">&nbsp;: Assure la connexion et le transfert d&rsquo;information des composants constituants le syst&egrave;me</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Capteurs photor&eacute;sistance (LDR)</span></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">&nbsp;: Un </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">semi-conducteur qui diminue sa r&eacute;sistance &eacute;lectrique lorsqu&#39;il est expos&eacute; &agrave; la lumi&egrave;re</span></span></span>. On a utilis&eacute; 4 photor&eacute;sistances plac&eacute;s sur les quatre sommets du panneau et indiquent de quel c&ocirc;t&eacute; il y a une forte concentration lumineuse </span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Ecran LCD 16*2</span></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">&nbsp;: Affiche la position du soleil et l&rsquo;angle d&rsquo;orientation du soleil &nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Carton&nbsp;: </span></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Utilis&eacute; pour fabriquer les diff&eacute;rentes pi&egrave;ces (Bras + Base) du syst&egrave;me</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom:solid #a2a9b1 1.0pt; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n<p style=\"border:none; margin-top